data.message: Design workflow quick reference: 1) Colors: Realtime Colors → Coolors → WebAIM, 2) Gradients: CSS Gradient or Mesher, 3) Effects: ui.glass + Smooth Shadows, 4) Icons: Lucide (React) or Phosphor (weights), 5) Illustrations: unDraw or Storyset, 6) Components: shadcn/ui, 7) Reference: Material Design 3.
